        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Samantha Pang <samantha.pang@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: Reading, display, and analysis of dual RNA sequence based on host and pathogen data. Takes csv files with gene counts and runs a differential expression analysis on them.
